      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just not the same anymore. i'm always the one needing help, needing someone to drive me or help with the bills or just... check on me. i see how tired they look when they come over. i just wish i could go quietly so they could finally have their lives back without worrying about me every single second. it feels like it would be much more peaceful for everyone if i just wasn't around.",
